item.title: Search
item.description: Search guide Use * asterisks before or after words to expand results. Do not use the asterisks if looking for exact words. Say we want to find anything with the word Ginger Ging* will find Ginger or other words that start with Ging Ginger* won’t work. If you’re looking for Gingerella though, well, knock yourself out :P Simply search Ginger without asterisk if looking for Ginger ZooBerry is a statically-generated website, which means performing a site search on Google.
